<emphasis id="B921EB625553FFBF528DB98FFED7FD53" bold="true" italics="true" pageId="57" pageNumber="58">
Key to genera of 
<taxonomicName id="4C554CF35553FFBF5390B98CFDA0FD39" authorityName="Latreille" authorityYear="1802" box="[416,538,661,690]" class="Insecta" family="Tenebrionidae" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="57" pageNumber="67" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="tribe" tribe="Pimeliini">Pimeliini</taxonomicName>
